
                     -=[ Ranks ]=-

   The following is a listing of all Ranks within the Knights.


Rank    
 1           Squire
 2           Shield-Bearer
 3           Knight Errant
 4           Knight
 5           Commander
 6           High Commander
 7           Marshall
 8           Grand Marshall

These ranks are gained through deeds of honor and courage. They 
are necessary to have in order to use your powers and skills 
effectively.


 Related Topics: spell_list, titles, levels

 